metadata.description:
Joe Ji rang the alarm and lowered his eyes to see that he, too, had nothing on.



Combined with the sudden emergence of trivial dream fragments, the body feeling of falling apart, and the pain of tearing somewhere, Ji Qiao really realized that there was no big film, but there was that kind of film



He was in bed, but it wasn't a ghost, it was someone else.
